		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;line-height:100%;border-bottom:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;font-family:Calibri;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">The Board of the Corporation does not know of any matters for action by stockholders at the Annual Meeting other than the matters described in the Notice of Annual Meeting.&nbsp;&nbsp;However, the enclosed Proxy will confer discretionary authority with respect to matters which are not known to the Board at the time of the printing hereof and which may properly come before the meeting.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is the intention of the persons named in the Proxy to vote such Proxy with respect to such matters in accordance with their best judgment.</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;line-height:100%;border-top:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;font-family:Calibri;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;">The entire expense of preparing, assembling and mailing the enclosed material will be borne by the Corporation.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition to using the mail, directors, officers and employees of the Bank acting on behalf of the Corporation, and without extra compensation, may solicit proxies in person, by telephone or by facsimile.</font><font style="display: inline;">&nbsp;</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;text-align:center;line-height:100%;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">STOCKHOLD</font><a name="StockholderProposals"></a><font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">ER PROPOSALS</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;border-bottom:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;">Any proposals of stockholders intended to be submitted at the 2019 Annual Meeting of Stockholders under SEC Rule 14a-8 must be received by the Chairman of the Board or the President no later than November 16, 2018 in order to be considered for inclusion in the proxy statement and form of proxy for such meeting under SEC Rule 14a-8.&nbsp; </font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;border-top:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;border-bottom:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;">Under the Corporation&#x2019;s bylaws, a stockholder must follow certain procedures to nominate persons for election as directors or to introduce an item of business at a meeting of stockholders. These procedures provide, generally, that stockholders desiring to make nominations for directors, or to bring a proper subject of business before the 2019 Annual Meeting, must do so by a written notice timely delivered to the Corporation&#x2019;s Secretary generally not later than December 14, 2018.</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;border-top:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;border-bottom:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;">If the Corporation is not notified of a matter to be brought before the 2019 Annual Meeting by December 14, 2018 or if a matter is omitted from the proxy statement or proxy pursuant to SEC Rule 14a-8, then the proxy may provide discretionary authority to management of the Corporation to vote against such matter.&nbsp;&nbsp; </font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;border-top:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;">Nothing in this proxy statement will be deemed to require us to include in our proxy statement and proxy relating to an annual meeting any stockholder proposal that does not meet all of the requirements for inclusion established by the SEC in effect at the </font><font style="display: inline;">time such proposal is received.</font><font style="display: inline;">&nbsp;</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;text-align:center;line-height:100%;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">INTERNET AV</font><a name="InternetAvailabilityofProxyMaterials"></a><font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">AILABILITY OF PROXY MATERIALS</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt;text-align:center;border-bottom:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;line-height:100%;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">Important Notice Regarding the Availability of Proxy Materials for the Annual Meeting of Stockholders to be held on</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;text-align:center;border-top:1pt none #D9D9D9 ;line-height:100%;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">April 17, 2018</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;">The Company&#x2019;s proxy statement and form of proxy for its 2018 Annual Meeting of Stockholders and its 2017 Annual Report on Form 10-K to security holders is available at http://www.cstproxy.com/fnbli/2018.</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;">For driving directions to The Carltun, the location of the annual meeting, please go to http://www.thecarltun.com.</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;text-align:center;line-height:100%;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">ANNUAL REPOR</font><a name="AnnualReportstoStockholders"></a><font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">TS TO STOCKHOLDERS</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;font-weight:bold;">Consolidated financial statements for the Corporation are included in the Corporation&#x2019;s 2017 Annual Report on Form 10-K which was mailed with this Proxy Statement.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition, copies of the 2017 Annual Report on Form 10-K as filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission will be sent to any stockholder upon written request without charge.&nbsp;&nbsp;Such request should be directed to Mark D. Curtis, Senior Executive Vice President, Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer, at the Corporation&#x2019;s principal office, 10 Glen Head Road, Glen Head, New York 11545.</font>
		</p>
		<p style="margin:0pt;line-height:100%;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 10pt">
			<font style="display: inline;">&#xFEFF;</font>
		</p>
